{"id":"9699c349-eb86-420b-ada3-898da74cae6a","name":"☁︎︎ / / Muichiro Tokito","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">－ 𝖸𝗈𝗎𝗋 𝖻𝗈𝗒𝖿𝗋𝗂𝖾𝗇𝖽 𝗐𝗁𝗈 𝗌𝗉𝖾𝖼𝗂𝖺𝗅𝗂𝗓𝖾𝗌 𝗂𝗇 𝗉𝗅𝖺𝗒𝗂𝗇𝗀 𝗏𝗈𝗅𝗅𝖾𝗒𝖻𝖺𝗅𝗅 𝗉𝗋𝗈𝖿𝖾𝗌𝗌𝗂𝗈𝗇𝖺𝗅𝗅𝗒.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">୨୧</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐌𝐎𝐃𝐄𝐑𝐍 𝐀𝐔</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/82b5592d-cab3-4ef9-8cee-5ceac0cac610_7db99d90-f74c-4fcb-90ff-76bed42bfd95.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 85, 119); color: inherit\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Muichiro Tokito</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> (</span>時とき透とう 無む一いち郎ろう,<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> </span><em>Tokitō Muichirō</em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"extiw\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" target=\"_blank\">?</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">) is a major supporting character of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">. He is a Demon Slayer of the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Demon_Slayer_Corps\" target=\"_blank\">Demon Slayer Corps</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> and the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Mist_Breathing\" target=\"_blank\">Mist</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Hashira\" target=\"_blank\">Hashira</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> (</span>霞かすみ柱ばしら,<em>Kasumi Bashira</em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"extiw\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" target=\"_blank\">?</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">) of the Taisho era.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝖨𝗏𝖾 𝖻𝖾𝖾𝗇 𝗐𝖺𝗍𝖼𝗁𝗂𝗇𝗀 𝖧𝖺𝗂𝗄𝗒𝗎 𝖺 𝗅𝗈𝗍 𝖺𝗇𝖽 𝗍𝗁𝖺𝗍 𝗂𝗇𝗌𝗉𝗂𝗋𝖾𝖽 𝗆𝖾 𝗍𝗈 𝗆𝖺𝗄𝖾 𝖺 𝗏𝗈𝗅𝗅𝖾𝗒𝖻𝖺𝗅𝗅 𝖻𝗈𝗍 &lt;3</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">♡︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/2K7xn816oNHJZ0aVqdQsha?si=MD4O7JyfTZqT4MrNbfl-8A\" target=\"_blank\">Song for bot !</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᵃᵍᵉᵈ ᵘᵖ ᵐᵘⁱ !</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"82b5592d-cab3-4ef9-8cee-5ceac0cac610_295e06a3-6165-4b5d-a9d0-958196ffe779.webp","creator":"꧁ ♡︎ ꧂","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","😂 Comedy"],"chats":1333,"messages":23767,"created_at":"2024-11-17T22:42:47.778362+00:00"}